    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience The Pale Beyond’s hand-drawn art inspired by Victorian etchings. The Digital Artbook is a 96 page digital artbook detailing the characters and environments of The Pale Beyond.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168790/extras/47bb07a2b2cce86089fb2780ee2eff96.webp?t=1757524347\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168790/extras/47bb07a2b2cce86089fb2780ee2eff96.poster.avif?t=1757524347\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=338 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring character art, ship design, environment art (and the sled dogs!) by Jess Campbell, Katie Noble, Ethan Mclean and Nadine McLaughlin, the book offers insights on the development and an intimate look at the Temperance and her crew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>To access the art book:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Right click<strong> The Pale Beyond</strong> in your Steam Library</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select <strong>Manage</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select <strong>Browse Local Files</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open the <strong>Artbook</strong> folder</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The art book will be downloaded to this Steam folder in PDF format.</p>",
